name: SF.gov Forms template
description:
This is a form template of SF.gov government services that we used for a quick prototype of how the form is written. Editors can easily update the component types, labels, and error messages. We also use this tool to map out the entire form flow and view form page by page.


We will be updating our form styles later this year and there will be more updates to this form template in the near future. We always welcome your thoughts, please comment below on the community page.
